  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"customer-4\"\n        title=\"customer-4\"\n        src=\"/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/4b190/customer-4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/e07e9/customer-4.jpg 200w,\n/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/066f9/customer-4.jpg 400w,\n/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/4b190/customer-4.jpg 800w,\n/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/e5166/customer-4.jpg 1200w,\n/static/f50446d52323af537b40adb24f1baadb/eea4a/customer-4.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></li>\n<li>_</li>\n<li>주문이 완료되면 주문 내역을 다시 한 번 확인할 수 있습니다.<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/eea4a/customer-5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"customer-5\"\n        title=\"customer-5\"\n        src=\"/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/4b190/customer-5.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/e07e9/customer-5.jpg 200w,\n/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/066f9/customer-5.jpg 400w,\n/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/4b190/customer-5.jpg 800w,\n/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/e5166/customer-5.jpg 1200w,\n/static/23844384c1fd10d567128cffec6a0655/eea4a/customer-5.j